N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 604.4 - Exhibits

State Regulations

Certified copies of all resolutions and orders of the board
of supervisors bearing on the matter must be appended as exhibits; together
with any pertinent maps, reports or papers which the board desires to call to
the attention of the commission. Notes
